    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies optional things that one can do with "ni"
   URIs and related names.  Those include an additional hash algorithm
   for handling dynamic content, some specific query-strong parameters
   for ni URIs and a mechanism for embedding ni URIs into QR codes.</t>
    </abstract>
